data.description: Welcome Home! This 3-4 bedroom home offers three baths. Located in the Hospital and School area, this home has had many updates and ready for you. Enter the home into the living room that has a fireplace with built in bookshelves.The updated dining room is next with access out to a private patio that is perfect for relaxing on those warm or cool nights. Off the dining room enter the modern kitchen with stainless appliances and room for a table. The kitchen was updated in 2020. Next up is a bonus room with a bathroom off of it, a den that could be used as a fourth bedroom or office. The bonus room also has access to the second floor with the back staircase. Second floor offers 3 bedroom and 2 full bathrooms. From the front/main stairwell you'll come to the first 2 bedrooms and full bath. One bedroom offers a huge walk in closet and dressing room. At the end of the hall you'll find the master suite. This is where the access for the back stairwell can be found. This home has an amazing layout. The full basement is where laundry is located, storage room, extra space for workout/home gym or crafting/hobby room. Off the basement, walk into the three car garage. Call today!
